    slug: "complete-vacation-deals-glossary",
    title: "The Complete Vacation Deals Glossary: Terms You Need to Know",
    metaTitle: "Vacation Deals Glossary | Essential Terms A-Z",
    metaDescription: "Every vacation deal term explained in plain English. From timeshare jargon to booking lingo, this glossary has you covered. No industry experience needed.",
